TITLE: Initializing Turnkey EIP-1193 Provider
DESCRIPTION: Complete initialization process for the Turnkey EIP-1193 Provider, including setting up the WebauthnStamper, TurnkeyClient, retrieving organization details, and configuring the chain settings.
