TITLE: Initializing IframeStamper for Recovery and Auth in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to initialize the IframeStamper, inject a credential bundle, and create a new HTTP client for Recovery and Auth flows. It uses the @turnkey/iframe-stamper and @turnkey/http packages.
