TITLE: Initializing and Managing Embedded Keys in Iframe
DESCRIPTION: Example showing how to create a TurnkeyBrowserSDK instance, initialize an iframe client, and manage embedded keys using clearEmbeddedKey() and initEmbeddedKey() functions.
