TITLE: Initializing TurnkeyClient
DESCRIPTION: Example of initializing the TurnkeyClient with API key stamper and environment variables
SOURCE: https://github.com/tkhq/sdk/blob/main/docs/markdown/@turnkey/http/documents/TurnkeyClient.mdx#2025-04-16_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
