TITLE: Verifying Turnkey Stamp Signature using ECDSA and SHA-256 in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This function verifies a signature from a Turnkey stamp using ECDSA and SHA-256. It takes a public key, signature, and signed data as input, and returns a boolean indicating whether the signature is valid. If the signature is invalid, it throws an error.
