TITLE: Initializing Iframe Client
DESCRIPTION: This snippet explains how to initialize the Iframe client to interact with hosted iframes for sensitive operations. It specifies the iframeContainer and iframeUrl parameters, demonstrating interaction with an Email Auth process.
