TITLE: Migration Changes for ethers v6 - Balance Check
DESCRIPTION: Example showing how to migrate balance checking code from ethers v5 to v6. The getBalance method is moved from signer to provider and requires an address parameter.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tkhq/sdk/blob/main/packages/ethers/CHANGELOG.md#2025-04-16_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
// before
const balance = await connectedSigner.getBalance();

// after
// first get the address
const address = await connectedSigner.getAddress()
// then pass it in
const balance = await connectedSigner.provider?.getBalance(address)
```

