DESCRIPTION: Commands for cloning the Turnkey SDK repository, installing dependencies, and building the source code. This prepares the environment for running the export-in-node example.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tkhq/sdk/blob/main/examples/export-in-node/README.md#2025-04-16_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
$ git clone https://github.com/tkhq/sdk
$ cd sdk/
$ corepack enable  # Install `pnpm`
$ pnpm install -r  # Install dependencies
$ pnpm run build-all  # Compile source code
$ cd examples/export-in-node/
```

