TITLE: Defining Activity Types and Results in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet defines complex TypeScript types for various blockchain activities and their results. It includes enums for activity status and types, as well as detailed result structures for different operations like creating API keys, signing transactions, and managing policies.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tkhq/sdk/blob/main/docs/markdown/@turnkey/sdk-server/index/namespaces/TurnkeyApi/variables/approveActivity.mdx#2025-04-16_snippet_2

